contentrichtext.text: '''Zyklon''' is the German word for [[cyclone]]. It may also refer to: * [[Zyklon]], a Norwegian industrial blackened death metal band * Zyklon A (active ingredient: [[methyl cyanoformate]]), a pesticide * [[Zyklon B]], a pesticide ultimately used by Nazi Germany in gas chambers * [[Zyklon-B (band)]], a Norwegian black metal band featuring former Emperor members * [[Zyklon (comics)]], fictional villain created by [[DC Comics]] * [[Zyklon (roller coaster)]], a former roller coaster at Morey's Piers {{disambig}}
